Package: bosc
Type: Package
Title: Behavioral Oscillation Scores and Phase Analysis
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Bradley", "Buchsbaum", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "brad.buchsbaum@gmail.com")
    )
Description: R port of the behavioral-oscillations MATLAB toolbox (Ter Wal et
    al.) for computing oscillation scores, surrogate tests, phase analyses, PPC
    metrics, clustering, and plotting for behavioral and neural time series.
    Methods are described in Ter Wal et al. (2021) <doi:10.1038/s41467-021-27323-3>.
License: CC BY 4.0
URL: https://github.com/bbuchsbaum/bosc
